How long can you walk a bulldog?
Just like people, no two dogs are the same. Some bulldogs will be resistant to more than mild exercise, while others will be ready to roam for miles (with plenty of water and chances to cool down, of course). Typically, though, this breed needs between 20 and 40 minutes of exercise every day
